Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:47.92,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}起立！敬禮！鎖定！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:52.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}曾經想著總有人會解決
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:58.38,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}多少帶著旁觀的心態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:01.06,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}然而
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:06.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請告訴不成熟的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:11.85,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}何時才能擊倒你這個不落的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:17.35,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}只要挑戰 可能性是half＆half
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:22.34,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}Mr.teacher請看著迷茫的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:27.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}為了你比任何人都認真學習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:33.57,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}殺意就是唯一給你的信息
